\begin_layout Standard
Hint:
 考虑椭圆切点处的切线方程为
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\frac{x_{0}x}{a^{2}}+\frac{y_{0}y}{b^{2}}=\pm1,\quad\frac{x_{1}x}{a^{2}}+\frac{y_{1}y}{b^{2}}=\pm1,
\]

\end_inset

四条切线构成正方形,
 根据平行线间距公式推出 
\begin_inset Formula $x_{0}^{2}=x_{1}^{2}$
\end_inset

 较为容易.
 所以内切于正方形的椭圆长短轴在其对角线内,
 转换坐标系,
 考虑椭圆的四组切线方程
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\frac{x_{0}x}{a^{2}}+\frac{y_{0}y}{b^{2}}=\pm1,\quad\frac{x_{0}x}{a^{2}}-\frac{y_{0}y}{b^{2}}=\pm1,
\]

\end_inset

两切线垂直得到 
\begin_inset Formula $b^{4}x_{0}^{2}=a^{4}y_{0}^{2}$
\end_inset

,
 从而切线间距
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
d=\sqrt{2\left(a^{2}+b^{2}\right)}
\]

\end_inset

应为正方形固定边长.
 椭圆周长
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
l=4\int_{0}^{\pi/2}\sqrt{a^{2}\sin^{2}t+b^{2}\cos^{2}t}\ud t & \xlongequal{t\to\pi/2-t}4\int_{0}^{\pi/2}\sqrt{a^{2}\cos^{2}t+b^{2}\sin^{2}t}\ud t\\
 & \xlongequal{\text{合并两个积分}}4\int_{0}^{\pi/2}\frac{\sqrt{a^{2}\sin^{2}t+b^{2}\cos^{2}t}+\sqrt{a^{2}\cos^{2}t+b^{2}\sin^{2}t}}{2}\ud t\\
 & \le4\int_{0}^{\pi/2}\sqrt{\frac{\left(a^{2}\sin^{2}t+b^{2}\cos^{2}t\right)+\left(a^{2}\cos^{2}t+b^{2}\sin^{2}t\right)}{2}}\ud t=\pi,
\end{align*}

\end_inset

其中不等式为幂平均不等式,
