 & \qquad=\frac{1}{2R}\iint_{\Sigma}yz(y-z)(x-2R)+xz(z-x)y+xy(x-y)z\ud S\\
 & \qquad=-\iint_{\Sigma}yz(y-z)\ud S=-\iint_{\Sigma}y^{2}z\ud S-\iint_{\Sigma}yz^{2}\ud S.
